      <title>OpenAI 与洛斯阿拉莫斯合作测试 AI 对实验室工作的价值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/openai-partners-with-los-alamos-to-test-ai-s-value-for-lab-work</link>
